---
title: BBQ Double Chicken Burger & Onion Chutney with Creamy Slaw & Fries
description: Juicy chicken seasoned with a barbecue zap is a smokey dream come true for your taste buds. Place it in a fresh bun, serve with classic fries and glaze the chicken with an onion chutney to elevate these burgers to the next level.

